			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Quillmane is a RANDOM spawn, he is supposed to appear once every week and a half to two weeks from what I have heard doing a lot of research on the Cazic-Thule server. From what I have heard, Quillmane is able to be taken down by a group of 5 or 6 lvl 25 and up characters, and spawns near the Aviak Village in the South Karana area. The cloak is a one in ten chance, the leggings mentioned in a previous post being the other loot item. Quillmane looks like Pegasus, and flies around in the area of the village. General consensus is that Quillmane is roughly level 30, I have not been able to come across any info on how hard Quillmane hits or if it casts any spells etc. I will post more if I find any info.
			</font>
	
