			After reading about this cloak and thinking I could get it only in my wildest dreams I fell into some luck the other day. I am a 25th level druid and was hunting at the aviak village in south karana, I was walking down the ramp when I saw this magnificent beast standing in the field. I immediately jumped off the city and rooted it. I then cast a DoT on it and nuked him to death. He conned red at level 25, but did not resist my spells. As for the item, it is one of the best I've ever seen.<BR>
